    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Demo is limited to the first 10 levels, join our Discord server to give us feedback &amp; hear about updates first!</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meowmentum</strong> is a first-person speedrunning platformer in which you must finish speed trials as fast as possible to become a full-fledged catmage! 🐈🧙‍♂️ What are you waiting for? Go get your name on the leaderboards MEOW~!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/78ba714849dd3c2f6c2ca9dcacae18e3.avif?t=1770010937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras_big/78ba714849dd3c2f6c2ca9dcacae18e3.webp?t=1770010937 width=1560 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your newly-found powers of Meowmentum and harness the potential of paw-kour! Run on walls, slide down ramps, and dash through magic orbs to keep going faster!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/6dd991d9267751806ef9ffe06af1cc87.poster.avif?t=1770010937\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/6dd991d9267751806ef9ffe06af1cc87.webm?t=1770010937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/6dd991d9267751806ef9ffe06af1cc87.mp4?t=1770010937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/c6f18b9a2e07cb2cc90fd7175b24c2c2.avif?t=1770010937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras_big/c6f18b9a2e07cb2cc90fd7175b24c2c2.webp?t=1770010937 width=1560 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove yourself worthy by completing the Elder Catmages' speed trials! Discover secret shortcuts and movement techniques as you paw through each trial!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/fe0d48c1bfb1ca42da82a0852a1b81c4.poster.avif?t=1770010937\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/fe0d48c1bfb1ca42da82a0852a1b81c4.webm?t=1770010937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/fe0d48c1bfb1ca42da82a0852a1b81c4.mp4?t=1770010937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/c16c9969695027ca3613094944e9c640.avif?t=1770010937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras_big/c16c9969695027ca3613094944e9c640.webp?t=1770010937 width=1560 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect meow-zmerizing medals and race against Catmages worldwide! Will you dominate the leaderboards and become a master of Meowmentum? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/e3bd5e900a4ad23ddf7fee84dc41f5f5.poster.avif?t=1770010937\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/e3bd5e900a4ad23ddf7fee84dc41f5f5.webm?t=1770010937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/e3bd5e900a4ad23ddf7fee84dc41f5f5.mp4?t=1770010937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras/9ec58ed7e3f4c84a7c5d580b11d1d2e0.avif?t=1770010937\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236850/extras_big/9ec58ed7e3f4c84a7c5d580b11d1d2e0.webp?t=1770010937 width=1560 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello! We are a team of 8 part-time developers aiming to create the best magical cat speedrunner in the world! We sincerely hope you enjoy our game, in whatever capacity that may be. Wanna chat with us? JOIN OUR DISCORD SERVER!! Thank you &lt;3   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>All social links are to the right of (PC) or above this description (Mobile).</i></p>",
